text: Carla van Usen is a Dutch water polo player. She competed for the Dutch women's national water polo team in the 1998 World Aquatics Championships, and 1997 Women's World Cup Championship. == References == == Other websites== * 9 Jul 2000: Carla Van Usen #6 of the Netherlands swims getty Category:Dutch water polo players Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
